===Etymology===
From Middle English ''[[moderat]]'' < Latin ''[[moderatus|moderātus]]'' (past principle of ''[[moderari|moderārī]]'', “to moderate”)

===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|/mŏd'ər-ĭt/ ''(adjective)'', /mŏd'ə-rāt'/ ''(verb)''}}

===Adjective===
'''moderate'''

# Not [[excessive]]; acting in [[moderation]]

